text: Chen Yiwen (born 15 June 1999) is a Chinese diver. She participated at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, winning a medal. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female divers Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in diving Category:Asian Games medalists in diving Category:Divers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for China Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games
